Available Tools: share_file | set_permissions | get_shared_link | revoke_access | list_collaborators
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "file_id": "string", "user_email": "string", "permission": "view|comment|edit", "expires_at": "string" }
Response Schema: { "file_id": "string", "shared_link": "string", "collaborators": [{ "email": "string", "permission": "string" }] }
---
Question: Revoke access for brian.thompson@globalinc.com on the Q4 sales report and show me who still has access.
Call: { "func_call": "revoke_access", "file_id": "file_7712_sales_q4", "user_email": "brian.thompson@globalinc.com", "permission": "edit", "expires_at": "" }
Response: { "file_id": "file_7712_sales_q4", "shared_link": "https://storage.example.com/s/q4s9a2", "collaborators": [{ "email": "jessica.park@globalinc.com", "permission": "edit" }, { "email": "tom.harris@globalinc.com", "permission": "view" }] }

